title: Andy Warstar - 03/25/07 Nim FM 102.3 - Complete Show
description:
Here&#039;s Andy Warstar&#039;s first Australian radio show/performances all nicely edited

into separate mp3 tracks. Hosted by Andy&#039;s friend Warwick (who was never without

a beer in his hand the whole time...) The Aussies were naturally quite curious

about an oddity like Andy, and Aussie-American and a punk folker to boot.

This show is a rare collectible.
